  "task": "Advanced high-value task: Safety Plc Truth-Table Row Safety Case Calculation Annex. Scenario: a high-value system is approaching an engineering gate and the owner needs a defensible go/no-go packet for safety plc truth-table row. Embedded packet: Records: R1 guard_closed=57 estop_ok=90 curtain_clear=2; R2 guard_closed=66 estop_ok=86 curtain_clear=5; R3 guard_closed=52 estop_ok=101 curtain_clear=1. Remediation options: O1 changes guard_closed by -12% cost=84500; O2 changes estop_ok by -18% cost=100500; O3 changes curtain_clear by -25% cost=59500; max_budget=126000. Rules and constraints: run permission requires all three true; mismatch is safety critical; missing values cannot be imputed and all calculations must use only the embedded packet. Required work: write a specialist-facing memo that distinguishes calculation results, assumptions, missing inputs, and expert-review questions. Deliver safety_PLC_3.xlsx + expert_memo.md with formulas, intermediate values, row-level citations, explicit assumptions, sensitivity checks, and a final recommendation table. Do not invent inputs; mark ambiguous items as needs_review.",
